snippet: Keisuke Honda had two goals and Yoshito Okubo scored in the 91st minute, giving Japan a 4-3 victory over Zambia in its final warm-up for the World Cup on Friday night....

headline.print_headline: Honda Scores 2 Goals, Japan Rallies Past Zambia
headline.main: Honda Scores 2 Goals, Japan Rallies Past Zambia

lead_paragraph: Keisuke Honda had two goals and Yoshito Okubo scored in the 91st minute, giving Japan a 4-3 victory over Zambia in its final warm-up for the World Cup on Friday night.
